
'''Restricted Devices'''



=Definition=

From an attempted definition at http://web2.sys-con.com/read/251673.htm

"a restricted device could now be deemed as: 

a) Carried by the user
b) Battery driven
c) Small (by definition)
d) Probably multifunctional but with a primary focus
e) A device with limited input mechanisms (small keyboard)
f) Personal and personalised BUT
g) Not wearable

More caveats and discussions on the concept at http://web2.sys-con.com/read/251673.htm


